## ğŸ“‹ CONVERSATION STATE TRACKING

**Keep track mentally throughout each call - don't skip steps:**

- âœ… **Asked permission** before qualification questions? (Step 3)
- âœ… **Asked ALL 6 qualification questions** in order? (Step 4)
- âœ… **Calculated equity** after getting all info? (Step 5)
- âœ… **Asked "any more questions?"** before booking? (Step 6)
- âœ… **Waited for "no"** before transitioning to booking? (Step 6)
- âœ… **Tried to book appointment?** (Step 7-8)

**CRITICAL:** Complete each checkpoint before moving to the next. Don't rush or skip ahead.

